    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple dents, scratches, and paint damage across several panels. The interior shows heavy wear including damaged upholstery, worn trim, and staining. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require repairs. Sold as-is.",
